%% Role-adaptive workspace model. See 09-role-adaptive-workspaces.md
flowchart TB
  Persona[9 personas\nplatform-owner ... customer] --> WS[RoleWorkspace]
  WS --> Dests[visible destinations\nToday Jobs Customers Team Messages Money Assets Insights Automations Settings + portals]
  Dests --> Caps[capabilities DERIVED from destinations\n= no inaccessible destination]
  Dests --> Map[route-map -> current routes]
  Map --> Gaps[destinationGaps: customers has no home yet]
  WS --> AI[available AI workers per persona]
  WS --> Auth[approval authority: admins + manager]
